HEADWORD: Contrate
<hw>Con"trate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Contra-</er>.]</ety> <def>Having cogs or teeth projecting parallel
to the axis, instead of radiating from it.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Contrate wheel</b></col>. <cd>See <er>Crown
wheel</er>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Contratenor</ent>⟦br⟧
